<TITLE>
Jipijka'm (Tcipitckaam, Chepechcalm)
</TITLE>

<META NAME="description" CONTENT="Information and legends about the Native American mythological figure Jipijka'm,
a horned serpent from the folklore of the Mi'kmaq tribe.">
